      <text>&lt;i&gt;NlATG1&lt;/i&gt; Gene Participates in Regulating Autophagy and Fission of Mitochondria in the Brown Planthopper, &lt;i&gt;Nilaparvata lugens&lt;/i&gt;.</text>
